Text: I am an archer here not a fighter!
Damn it all. I will not suffer fools again!
Regret facing me and rot in the Eighth Hell!
Please carry on in my stead.
You are no match to me.
Praiseworthy, but I will do better.
The fallen wind will rise up again.
Give up on these futile attempts.
Hey, you will make me sore later!
I will not stand for this, you hear?!
It seemth there is much to learn yet.
